Blue Stinger looks at the bots that she piled up on a platform. They were 
the autobots on the Ark (with the matrix and everything :), the maximal's 
only weak poing. :) She smiles. If they didn't have to worry about them, 
they could all fight much better. She smiles again. :)

She presses several buttons on her wrist and the platform starts humming. 
She pushes several more buttons and the autobots dissapear. :)

She grins and turns around. Only she would know where the bots are and only 
she knew how to get them back. She walks back up to Tygerhawk. "Ok, now 
we're all ready." She says, smiling.  :):)
